requirements:
serverMonitor: sun-java5 jre and jdk

install:
1. be root
2. unpack file
3. switch to the directory
4. edit startServerMonitor to your config

run:
1. ./startServerMonitor


Commandline Arguments for serverMonitor.jar  
-------------------------------------------- 
--help  displays help  
--host <RMI hostname>  
--port <RMI port>  
--service <RMI servicename>  
--sleeptime <threadsleeptime in ms>  
  
If no parameters are given default values will be used.  
Default values:  
  
host = localhost, port = 1099, service = simulation, sleeptime = 10000ms  
  
  
RMI servicesnames can be found in the Massim Server README.